Latent space image encoder/decoder

You can fdownload FLUX.1 VAE Model with Model manager by filename:
ae.safetensors

Text encoders loader

FLUX1 use two models for text encoding: 
CLIP_L (or its variants)
T5XXL (fp16 precision is better than fp8)

you can download them with model manager by filenames:
clip_l.safetensors
t5xxl_fp16.safetensors

Diffusion model loader

Weight dtype is simplest method of incresing speed and reducing VRAM requirements by decreasing precision of calculations and quality. 

RTX 40*0 supports fast calculation with fp8 precision and it's perfect solution to generate FLUX images in less that 20 seconds using less that 14Gb of VRAM.

you can download FLUX.1 in fp8 precision with Model manager by filename:
flux1-dev-fp8.safetensors
